{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "vermogenspeil-api-v1",
    "name": "Vermogenspeil API",
    "description": "MijnVermogen / Vermogenspeil REST API (v1) — **fase 2 afgerond (Auth0)**.\n\n**Auth-flow:**\n1. Register → Verify Email (token uit e-mail)\n2. Login via Django proxy → Auth0 tokens (`id_token`, `access_token`, `refresh_token`)\n3. Beveiligde endpoints: `Authorization: Bearer {{idToken}}`\n4. Refresh via `POST /auth/token/refresh/` met `{ \"refresh\": \"...\" }`\n\n**MFA:** Auth0-managed. Bij `mfa_required` op login: OTP/enroll via Auth0 in de frontend (niet via deze API). Reset MFA: `POST /auth/mfa/reset/` (ingelogd).\n\n**baseUrl:**\n- Lokaal: `http://localhost:8000/api/v1`\n- Render: `https://vermogenspeil-api.onrender.com/api/v1`",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:8000/api/v1",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "testEmail",
      "value": "test@example.com",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "testPassword",
      "value": "SecurePass123!",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "verificationToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "passwordResetToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "idToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "accessToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "refreshToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "mfaToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "System",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health Check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/health/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["health", ""]
            },
            "description": "Publiek endpoint. Verwacht `{\"data\":{\"status\":\"ok\"},...}`"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "Registratie, login (Auth0 via Django proxy), profiel, wachtwoord reset en MFA reset.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.test('Registration succeeded', () => {",
                  "        pm.expect(json.error).to.eql(null);",
                  "        pm.expect(json.data.email_verified).to.eql(false);",
                  "    });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{testEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{testPassword}}\",\n  \"first_name\": \"Jan\",\n  \"terms_accepted\": true\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/register/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "register", ""]
            },
            "description": "Maakt Auth0-user + Django-profiel aan. Wachtwoord min. 12 tekens. Geen tokens terug — verificatie vereist.\n\nLokaal: check backend terminal voor verificatie-e-mail (console backend)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Verify Email",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.test('Email verified', () => {",
                  "        pm.expect(json.data.email_verified).to.eql(true);",
                  "    });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"token\": \"{{verificationToken}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/verify-email/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "verify-email", ""]
            },
            "description": "Bevestig e-mail met token uit verificatie-e-mail (24u geldig).\n\nZet `verificationToken` in collection/environment variables."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Resend Verification",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{testEmail}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/resend-verification/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "resend-verification", ""]
            },
            "description": "Stuurt nieuwe verificatielink (alleen voor ongeverifieerde accounts). Geeft altijd 200 (geen e-mail enumeration)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('idToken', json.data.id_token);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.data.access_token);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', json.data.refresh_token);",
                  "    pm.test('Login succeeded', () => {",
                  "        pm.expect(json.error).to.eql(null);",
                  "        pm.expect(json.data.id_token).to.be.a('string');",
                  "        pm.expect(json.data.access_token).to.be.a('string');",
                  "    });",
                  "}",
                  "",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 403 && json.error === 'mfa_required') {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('mfaToken', json.data.mfa_token);",
                  "    pm.test('MFA required', () => {",
                  "        pm.expect(json.data.mfa_token).to.be.a('string');",
                  "    });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{testEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{testPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login", ""]
            },
            "description": "Login via Django → Auth0 password grant. Blokkeert ongeverifieerde users (`email_not_verified`).\n\nSucces: slaat `idToken`, `accessToken`, `refreshToken` op.\n\nMFA: bij `403 mfa_required` wordt `mfaToken` opgeslagen — voltooi login in de frontend (Auth0 OTP)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('idToken', json.data.id_token);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.data.access_token);",
                  "    if (json.data.refresh_token) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', json.data.refresh_token);",
                  "    }",
                  "    pm.test('Token refreshed', () => {",
                  "        pm.expect(json.data.id_token).to.be.a('string');",
                  "    });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refresh\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/token/refresh/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "token", "refresh", ""]
            },
            "description": "Vernieuwt Auth0 tokens via Django proxy. Body: `{ \"refresh\": \"...\" }`."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Me",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.test('Profile loaded', () => {",
                  "        pm.expect(json.data.email).to.be.a('string');",
                  "        pm.expect(json.data.email_verified).to.eql(true);",
                  "    });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{idToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/me/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "me", ""]
            },
            "description": "Profiel van ingelogde user. Vereist Auth0 `id_token` als Bearer token."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Password Reset Request",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{testEmail}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/password/reset/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "password", "reset", ""]
            },
            "description": "Stuurt wachtwoord-resetlink (1u geldig). Geeft altijd 200 (geen e-mail enumeration).\n\nToken uit e-mail → `passwordResetToken`."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Password Reset Validate Token",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/password/reset/{{passwordResetToken}}/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "password", "reset", "{{passwordResetToken}}", ""]
            },
            "description": "Valideert reset token. Retourneert e-mailadres bij geldige token."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Password Reset Confirm",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"password\": \"NewSecurePass123!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/password/reset/{{passwordResetToken}}/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "password", "reset", "{{passwordResetToken}}", ""]
            },
            "description": "Stelt nieuw wachtwoord in (Auth0 + Django token invalidatie). Min. 12 tekens."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "MFA Reset",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{idToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/mfa/reset/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "mfa", "reset", ""]
            },
            "description": "Verwijdert Auth0 MFA voor ingelogde user. Bij volgende login opnieuw enrollen."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
